111z2aZ9MDr3ogp6P7h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142111q3tBouKX6ShsWHzx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142112Z2Bp10hL46TiF3RJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142112ZgOIU3pueTJwH0rD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/sneaker/419397/vans-tuichuquanxinannahaimujingdianxilieyifugutiaowenqiangshihuigui/\" rel=\"nofollow\">为庆祝加州安纳海姆的第一家工厂店铺诞生 53 周年，Vans 推出安纳海姆经典系列。</a></strong></p><p>新系列包括 Era95 DX 和 Classic Slip-On 98 DX 两个鞋款，灵感皆源于 Vans 复古海报中的鞋款，鞋面采用重质帆布材质，以单色条纹印花图案呈现红、绿、蓝三种复古配色，搭配标志性的白色中底。该系列将于 5 月 1 日起发售。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142512zs1FXC4BWgE6Lphd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142514ZuprGmJ0gH4cMytA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142538A1BntzGO2H4FV36N.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201904301425447rfOG1cmhs5NKgzY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142544zoiLgQ6Ob0E3dqGP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142512c1QLm3oGDhvqtYpF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201904301425394dsI2izYjxbAkw17.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/419621/nepenthes-dazao-2019-chunxiazaoxingteji/\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本知名品牌集合店 Nepenthes 发布了2019 春夏造型特辑，主题为 “Anything But Strong”。</a></strong></p><p>该系列大片由造型师 Naoki Ikeda 主导，选用了<a href=\"http://www.nepenthes.co.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Nepenthes 旗下在售的</a> Needles、Engineered Garments 和 South2 West8 等品牌的服装进行搭配。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201904301429369Pf6zw75VyGecRm8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142937YdoQtZzNwD30XGEU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142936SAvNlygwQYPJ0jK9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142937DmaYwn7VNioMxUPk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142958QY56bfT0ouItg3EF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142958pPaLKJ8bQjkqeROy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142956zPwv7oZYO8sU3FIE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142956WbYG3QpVDOXhqmAc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142957pBFkY1ygPu03QLqS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142954pysxmlakPchrI1RL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142955MyRx1Scw28iK3Lm0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142956D8xFHyNp3lVM26Gw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142954Q8bIWO7CYNtf6AnT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430142957XgNOMCPeIrt7nEHo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://highxtar.com/palace-ss19-new-dose-of-color-and-lifestyle/?lang=en\" rel=\"nofollow\">伦敦滑板品牌 Palace 发布 2019 夏季系列 Lookbook。</a></strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430143137krOLKBTtHCgYxhcU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430143151K6NH8WagMcOVxypj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201904301432058bLVRAiYcsknw3Qu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430143224AfZdnqp0CLUJt9eo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430143224fn1FxEDcB5TtaHd2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190430143225T3eg5XKhZpojrizW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201904301432254MQvzdc13RhrZxOu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201904301432262hFVyiO0IExRe7Hs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201904301432288Els3w5kLTG7JD4Q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"j